.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, musical, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, folk, indie, disco
 1. the person drinking tea is the fan of disco##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of disco##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror    | scientific | musical        |
| Music-Genre           | indie         | pop  | disco       | folk         |

